}}'''日本自卫队驻吉布提据点'''（{{lang-ja|ジブチ共和国における自衛隊拠点}}）是[[日本自卫队|日本自卫队]]設立在[[吉布提|吉布提]]{{link-en|安布利|Ambouli}}附近的军事基地。这是日本自卫队第一个长期駐扎的海外基地。

== 背景 ==
2009年，为应对[[索馬利亞海盜|索馬利亞海盜]]，[[日本国会|日本国会]]通过了反海盗措施法。        

从2009年3月起，日本[[海上自衛隊|海上自衛隊]]向[[亞丁灣|亞丁灣]]部署了{{link-en|涟號護衛艦|JS Sazanami}}和[[村雨型護衛艦_(二代)|村雨型護衛艦]]<ref>[http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/03/14/japan.pirates/index.html?iref=nextin Japan destroyers set sail on anti-piracy mission April 20, 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/asiapcf/03/14/japan.pirates/index.html?iref=nextin |date=20180616203845 }} ''[[有线电视新闻网|有线电视新闻网]]'' Retrieved November 23, 2016</ref>。日本海上自卫队还在吉布提部署了两架[[P-3獵戶座海上巡邏機|P-3獵戶座海上巡邏機]]，不過这些飞机受美国海军管理的{{link-en|萊蒙尼爾營|Camp Lemonnier}}指揮<ref>[https://www.stratfor.com/analysis/japan-joining-anti-piracy-effort-somali-coast Japan: Joining the Anti-Piracy Effort off the Somali Coast May 28, 2009] {{Wayback|url=https://www.stratfor.com/analysis/japan-joining-anti-piracy-effort-somali-coast |date=20200518023705 }} Retrieved November 21, 2016</ref><ref>[https://theaviationist.com/2013/01/22/patrol-planes-pirates/ Here’s how Coalition Patrol Planes Hunt Somali Pirates in the Horn of Africa January 23, 2013] {{Wayback|url=https://theaviationist.com/2013/01/22/patrol-planes-pirates/ |date=20180914131624 }} ''The Aviationist'' Retrieved November 21, 2016</ref><ref>[http://www.mofa.go.jp/policy/piracy/ja_somalia_1210.html Japan's Actions against Piracy off the Coast of Somalia February 15, 2016] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mofa.go.jp/policy/piracy/ja_somalia_1210.html |date=20161209152854 }} ''[[日本外務省|日本外務省]]'' Retrieved November 21, 2016</ref>。

== 历史 ==
2011年，日本海上自卫队在吉布提建立了自己的軍事基地，並在基地內部署了180名士兵，這些士兵轮流驻扎4个月。軍事基地內有指挥部、膳宿设施和停机坪<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/world/2015-01/20/content_19353950.htm Japan eyes first overseas SDF long-term base in Djibouti January 20, 2015] {{Wayback|url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/world/2015-01/20/content_19353950.htm |date=20170803085912 }} ''[[中国日报|中国日报]]'' Retrieved November 23, 2016</ref>。 

